content" role="region" aria-labelledby=":r1:-header" style="max-height: 0px;"><div class="accordion-inner-content">Two things. Your home's value, built from what's actually selling on your street, and my five playbooks: pricing, marketing, negotiation, concierge, speed, the systems behind every Irvine home I sell. They're yours to keep whether or not we ever talk.</div></div></section></div><div class="d_block w_100% m_0_auto bd_none c_textBody [&amp;:last-child_button]:bd-b_none"><section data-expanded="false" class="m_0"><button type="button" data-expanded="false" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls=":r2:-content" id=":r2:-header" data-has-custom-icon="true" class="d_flex ai_center jc_space-between w_100% p_10px_40px_16px_0 bg-c_transparent bd_none cursor_pointer fs_14px md:fs_16px lh_24px md:lh_32px ta_left pos_relative bd-b_1px_solid_rgba(75,_92,_117,_0.1019607843) [&amp;[data-expanded=&quot;true&quot;]]:bd-b_none focus:ring_none [&amp;::before]:content_&quot;&quot; [&amp;::before]:pos_absolute [&amp;::before]:right_0 [&amp;::before]:w_12px [&amp;::before]:bdr_2px [&amp;::before]:h_2px [&amp;::before]:top_50% [&amp;::before]:trf_translateY(-50%) [&amp;::after]:content_&quot;&quot; [&amp;::after]:pos_absolute [&amp;::after]:right_5px [&amp;::after]:w_2px [&amp;::after]:bdr_2px [&amp;::after]:h_12px [&amp;::after]:top_50% [&amp;::after]:trf_translateY(-50%) [&amp;[data-expanded=&quot;true&quot;]::after]:d_none [&amp;[data-has-custom-icon=&quot;true&quot;]::before]:d_none [&amp;[data-has-custom-icon=&quot;true&quot;]::after]:d_none"><h3 class="flex_1 fw_400 fs_16px">Why do you give the playbooks away free?</h3><div class="pos_absolute right_0 d_flex ai_center jc_center w_20px h_20px"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M2 6L10 6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"></path><path class="faq-icon-vertical" d="M6 2L6 10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-lineca